        "id": 810928355,
        "number": 124,
        "title": "LeetCode169第三种算法缺陷",
        "state": "closed",
        "created_at": "2021-02-18T09:38:44Z",
        "updated_at": "2021-02-18T09:44:18Z",
        "closed_at": "2021-02-18T09:44:18Z",
        "author": "smalllc",
        "comments": 0,
        "labels": [],
        "assignees": [],
        "locked": false,
        "body": " public int majorityElement(int[] nums) {\r\n    int candidate = nums[0], count = 1;\r\n    for (int i = 1; i < nums.length; ++i) {\r\n      if (count == 0) {\r\n        candidate = nums[i];\r\n        count = 1;\r\n      } else if (nums[i] == candidate) {\r\n        count++;\r\n      } else{\r\n        count--;\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n    return candidate;\r\n  }\r\n求一个数组的众数，存在一个缺陷，缺陷为最后的else\r\n设定一个数组长度为M，如果存在此种关系 2N+3=M\r\n最开始的N全部存放为X,第二个N存放不等于X的任意数。此时count==0\r\n众数的最后结果其实取决与 最后三位数的。\r\n如{2，2，2，2，2，1，3，5，6，7，8，11，11，0}\r\n输出结果为11 ，但11只出现两次\r\n",
        "url": "https://github.com/MisterBooo/LeetCodeAnimation/issues/124"
    },
